object.customQuery:
select isnull(pms.opened_date, '9999-12-31')                                                                   as account_entered_dt,
       pms.risk_state                                                                                          as risk_state,
       convert(varchar(12), pms.claim_number)                                                                  as claim_number,
       pmc.cat_group_desc,
       pms."loss cause"                                                                                        as losscausecd,
       pms.sub_loss_cause,
       CASE
           WHEN pms.lob like '%HP%' then 'Homeowners'
           WHEN pms.lob like '%SBP%' then 'Businessowners'
           WHEN pms.lob like '%FP%' then 'Dwelling'
           when pms.lob like '%IMC%' then 'Inland Marine â€“ Commercial (IMC)'
           ELSE PMS.LOB END                                                                                    AS lob_desc,
       CASE
           WHEN pms.lob like '%HP%' then 'Personal'
           WHEN pms.lob like '%SBP%' then 'Commercial'
           WHEN pms.lob like '%FP%' then 'Personal'
           when pms.lob like '%IMC%' then 'Commercial'
           ELSE PMS.lob END                                                                                    AS lob_group_desc,
       isnull(pms.opened_date, '9999-12-31')                                                                   as opened_date,
       isnull(pms.closed_date, '9999-12-31')                                                                   as closed_date,
       isnull(pms.reported_date, '9999-12-31')                                                                 as reported_date,
       pmc.claim_type,
       case
           when pms.gross_recovery > 0 then abs(datediff(days, pms.closed_date, pms.opened_date))
           else 0 end                                                                                          as cycle_time_files_with_recovery,
       case
           when pms.gross_recovery <= 0 then abs(datediff(days, pms.closed_date, pms.opened_date))
           else 0 end                                                                                          as cycle_time_files_without_recovery,
       ltrim(rtrim(pms.status))                                                                                as status,
       case when pms.gross_recovery > 0 then 'Recovered' else 'Not Recovered' end                              as subro_success_status,
       0                                                                                                       as loss_paid_amt,
       pms.demand                                                                                              as demand,
       isnull(pms.total_subrogation_expenses, 0)                                                               as subro_expense_amt,
       isnull(pms.total_subrogation_expenses, 0)                                                               as allocated_loss_adjustment_expense,
       isnull(pms.gross_recovery, 0)                                                                           as gross_recovery,
       isnull(pms.deductible_returned, 0)                                                                      as deductible_returned,
       isnull(pms."net recovery", 0)                                                                           as net_recovery,
       'OpenedDt-Dashboard'                                                                                    as dashboard_indicator,
       pms.subrogation_examiner,
       pms.subrogation_legal_counsel
from dbo.pms_master_subrogation pms
         left join (select distinct a.claim_number, a.cat_group_desc, claim_type, b.accident_dt
                    from dbo.pms_master_claim a,
                         dbo.pms_fact_loss b
                    where a.claim_key = b.claim_key
                      and b.claim_type = 'Property') pmc
                   on pmc.claim_number = right(replicate('0', 12) + convert(varchar(12), pms.claim_number), 12) and
                      pms.loss_date = pmc.accident_dt
UNION ALL
select isnull(pfl.account_entered_dt, '9999-12-31') as account_entered_dt,
       'NA'                                         as risk_state,
       pfl.claim_number,
       pmc.cat_group_desc,
       'NA'                                         as losscausecd,
       'NA'                                         as sub_loss_cause,
       l.lob_display_desc                           AS lob_desc,
       l.lob_display_group_desc                     AS lob_group_desc,
       '8888-01-01'                                 as opened_date,
       '8888-01-01'                                 as closed_date,
       pfl.reported_dt                              as reported_date,
       'NA'                                         as claim_type,
       0                                            as cycle_time_files_with_recovery,
       0                                            as cycle_time_files_without_recovery,
       'NA'                                         as status,
       'NA'                                         as subro_success_status,
       sum(pfl.loss_paid_amt)                       as loss_paid_amt,
       0                                            as demand,
       0                                            as subro_expense_amt,
       0                                            as allocated_loss_adjustment_expense,
       0                                            as gross_recovery,
       0                                            as deductible_returned,
       0                                            as net_recovery,
       'OpenedDt-Dashboard'                         as dashboard_indicator,
       NULL                                         AS subrogation_examiner,
       NULL                                         AS subrogation_legal_counsel
from dbo.pms_fact_loss pfl
         left join dbo.pms_master_claim pmc on pfl.claim_key = pmc.claim_key
         left join dbo.pms_master_policy pmp on pfl.policy_key = pmp.policy_key
         left join dbo.lob_ref l on pmp.lob_desc = l.pms_lob_desc
where pfl.claim_type = 'Property'
  and pmc.cat_group_desc = 'Non-Cat'
group by pfl.account_entered_dt, pfl.claim_number, pmc.cat_group_desc, l.lob_display_desc, l.lob_display_group_desc,
         pfl.reported_dt
